'''Pojhi Kapoor''' ({{Lang-hi|<U+092A><U+094B><U+091D><U+0940> <U+0915><U+092A><U+0942><U+0930>}} {{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq|<U+067E><U+0648><U+062C><U+06BE> <U+0628><U+062C><U+0631><U+06AF> / <U+06A9><U+067E><U+0648><U+0631>  }}}}) is a village and part of Bhualpur Panchayat of [[Saran district]], [[Bihar]], India.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brandbihar.com/english/districts/saran/saran_marhourah_bhualpur_pojhi%20kapoor.html |title=Pojhi Kapoor Village Bhualpur Panchayat Marhourah Block, saran Bihar India |publisher=Brandbihar.com |date= |accessdate=2013-10-04}}</ref>

== Geography ==

Pojhi Kapoor  is located at {{coord|25.87|N|84.85|E|}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.getaddress.net/?latlng=25.8706227,84.8541869 |title=Get Address of Properties Near 25.8706227,84.8541869 |publisher=Getaddress.net |date= |accessdate=2013-10-04}}</ref> It has an average elevation of 36&nbsp;metres.

== Location ==

Pojhi Kapoor is about 15&nbsp;km from district headquarters [[Chhapra]].It falls under Bhualur Panchayat of [[Saran district]] .Garkha is nearest city.The village is well-connected by roads in all seasons. The nearest railway station is Chhapra and the nearest airport is [[Lok Nayak Jayaprakash Airport]], [[Patna]].

== Development Works(Presently Running) ==

*Water supply pipelines: Going to get equipped with Water supply pipelines for each home belongs to the premises of this village. This work is at last stage of its completion. Image of developmental works will be available soon.

== Demographics ==

{{As of|2011}} India [[census]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://censusindia.gov.in/PopulationFinder/Population_Finder.aspx |title=Census of India: Population Finder |publisher=Censusindia.gov.in |date= |accessdate=2013-10-04}}</ref> Pojhi Kapoor had a population of 4254. Males constitute 55% of the population and females 45%.

== Healthcare & Facilities ==

*There is a Government Hospital situated in Pojhi Kapoor providing round the clock medical facility to people of the area.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.getaddress.net/?latlng=25.869550243598322,84.86068367958069 |title=Get Address of Properties Near 25.869550243598322,84.86068367958069 |publisher=Getaddress.net |date= |accessdate=2013-10-04}}</ref>
*Electricity supply is available for an average duration of 18 Hour(s)/24 Hour(s). Timings for breakdown are as:4 P.M.-6 P.M. and 8 P.M.-10 P.M.

==Schools==
Pojhi Kapoor has three primary schools and one Higher Secondary School specially for girls affiliated to [[Bihar School Examination Board]].
*Sitaram Project Balika Uchhayatar(+2) Vidyalaya,Pojhi Kapoor
*Prathmik Vidyalya,Pojhi Kapoor
*Prathmik Kanya Vidyalya,Pojhi Buzurg
*Prathmik Vidyalya,Pojhi Buzurg

